  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><math><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mfenced open=\"|\" close=\"|\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfenced></math></p><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><math><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn></math></p><p>The given system of equations has one solution <math><mfenced><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow></mfenced></math>. What is the solution?</p>",
